hom_ext:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
theorem hom_ext {X Y : UniformSpace} {f g : «expr ⟶ » X Y} : (f : X → Y) = g → f = g :=
  subtype.eq
#align hom_ext hom_ext
extension_hom_val:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
@[simp]
theorem extension_hom_val {X : UniformSpace} {Y : CpltSepUniformSpace} (f : «expr ⟶ » X ((forget₂ _ _).obj Y)) (x) :
    (extension_hom f) x = completion.extension f x :=
  rfl
#align extension_hom_val extension_hom_val
extension_comp_coe:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≫ » -/
@[simp]
theorem extension_comp_coe {X : UniformSpace} {Y : CpltSepUniformSpace}
    (f : «expr ⟶ » (to_UniformSpace (CpltSepUniformSpace.of (completion X))) (to_UniformSpace Y)) :
    extension_hom («expr ≫ » (completion_hom X) f) = f :=
  by
  apply subtype.eq
  funext x
  exact congr_fun (completion.extension_comp_coe f.property) x
#align extension_comp_coe extension_comp_coe
completion_hom_val:
@[simp]
theorem completion_hom_val (X : UniformSpace) (x) : (completion_hom X) x = (x : completion X) :=
  rfl
#align completion_hom_val completion_hom_val
coe_of:
@[simp]
theorem coe_of (X : Type u) [uniform_space X] [complete_space X] [separated_space X] : (of X : Type u) = X :=
  rfl
#align coe_of coe_of
coe_mk:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_mk {X Y : UniformSpace} (f : X → Y) (hf : uniform_continuous f) : ((⟨f, hf⟩ : «expr ⟶ » X Y) : X → Y) = f :=
  rfl
#align coe_mk coe_mk
coe_id:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr𝟙» -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_id (X : UniformSpace) : ((«expr𝟙») X : X → X) = id :=
  rfl
#align coe_id coe_id
coe_comp:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≫ » -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_comp {X Y Z : UniformSpace} (f : «expr ⟶ » X Y) (g : «expr ⟶ » Y Z) : («expr ≫ » f g : X → Z) = g ∘ f :=
  rfl
#align coe_comp coe_comp
